restaurant.name: Dilli 17
restaurant.description: This restaurant serves North Indian cuisine which is known for its spicy indulgence and the rich aroma. The various ingredients and rich gravy preparation instantly give a soul-satisfying taste to the diners. It has a great ambiance and is ideal for Indian food eaters who like spending quality time with families who are equally in love with authentic Indian curry dishes.
restaurant.address: 49 C, Savitri Nagar, Main Road, Maharishi Dayanand Marg, Panchsheel Park, New Delhi

restaurant.name: Chinese Hut
restaurant.description: Chinese Hut is a F&B-Casual Dining outlet that offers a wide variety of Chinese cuisine. The restaurant has a cozy and inviting atmosphere, with comfortable seating and a warm, welcoming staff. The menu features a variety of dishes, from traditional Chinese favorites to modern interpretations of classic dishes. The restaurant also offers a selection of drinks, including beer, wine, and specialty cocktails. Chinese Hut is the perfect place to enjoy a delicious meal with friends and family. The restaurant is open for lunch and dinner, and offers take-out and delivery services. Whether you're looking for a quick bite or a full meal, Chinese Hut is the perfect place to satisfy your cravings.
restaurant.address: G6, Vardhaman Plaza, Lsc Pocket B, Vasundhara Enclave, New Delhi

restaurant.name: Keventers - Milkshakes & Desserts
restaurant.description: Keventers is a popular chain of cafe joints specializing in offering deliciously flavored milkshakes and other beverages. The place offers an economical menu and an exclusive range of milkshakes to choose from. Every shake they serve is freshly prepared using the finest milk products and authentic flavors. Keventers has a number of outlets located spread in the city. This outlet is located in Aggarwal Millenium Tower in Netaji Subhash Place, Delhi.
restaurant.address: My Square Hari Singh Road, Select Citywalk, New Delhi

restaurant.name: Wat-a-Burger!
restaurant.description: Wat-a-Burger! is a fast food restaurant specializing in burgers and other classic American cuisine. With its fun and quirky name, Wat-a-Burger! offers a unique dining experience for customers looking for delicious and satisfying food. Their menu features a variety of juicy burgers, along with sides such as French fries, onion rings, and milkshakes. Wat-a-Burger! uses only high-quality ingredients, including fresh buns, beef patties, and toppings, to create a delicious and memorable burger experience. With its casual and friendly atmosphere, Wat-a-Burger! is a popular spot for families, friends, and solo diners alike. Whether you're in the mood for a quick bite or a sit-down meal, Wat-a-Burger! has something for everyone.
restaurant.address: O-8, Gf, Adjacent Patanjali Store, JMD Kohinoor Mall, New Delhi
